dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map: Scala milliarium.
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, territorial boundaries of the tribes of Israel, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Illustrations of settlements and coats of arms throughout.
Appears in Fuller's A Pisgah-sight of Palestine. London : John Williams, 1650.
